data.description: Elegant entertainers home in highly sought after Covered Bridge Plantation. 5 bedroom, 3 bath, bonus room, eat in kitchen, breakfast room and formal dining. The entry two story foyer boasts a grand entrance into engineered hardwood floors through the entry kitchen and dining areas. Upgraded and customized features, wainscoting, crown molding, custom ceiling features. Oversized lot with private backyard oasis, 23k gallon in ground pool with waterfall feature and slide, and exceptional space for entertaining. Home is located in top district and boasts a private trail to award winning Marlow elementary school. Home features exceptional master suite with open seating area and two walk-in closets, multiple storage and large attic space.
